diamonds = sns.load_dataset("diamonds")
sns.set()
sns.set_context('notebook')

import pandas as pd

cuttype = pd.CategoricalDtype(['Fair','Good','Very Good','Premium','Ideal'],ordered=True)
claritytype=pd.CategoricalDtype(['SI1', 'SI2', 'VS1', 'VS2', 'VVS1', 'VVS2', 'I1', 'IF'],ordered=True)

claritytype

diamonds['cut']=diamonds.cut.astype(cuttype)
diamonds['color']=diamonds.color.astype('category')
diamonds['clarity']=diamonds.clarity.astype(claritytype)
